          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Severus of Edessa. A Catena Patrum, or Selections from the Writings of the Fathers, so arranged as to form a continuous commentary on the greater part of the Scriptures of the Old and New Testaments. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 28 items.</note>
